## CSS View Transition Animations
<augment_code_snippet path="01-CSS-Wizard-Foundation/building-website-from-scratch/style.css" mode="EXCERPT">
```css
/* Enhanced view transitions for card filtering */
::view-transition-old(root) {
 animation-duration: 0.4s;
}

::view-transition-new(root) {
 animation-duration: 0.4s;
}

/* Custom animations for mushroom cards */
[style*="view-transition-name: mushroom-card"]::view-transition-old(mushroom-card) {
 animation: slide-out-down 0.3s ease-in forwards;
}

[style*="view-transition-name: mushroom-card"]::view-transition-new(mushroom-card) {
 animation: slide-in-up 0.3s ease-out forwards;
}
```
</augment_code_snippet>

## What this fancy animation system provides:

1. **Unique Identity**: Each card now has a unique `view-transition-name` (like `mushroom-card-mushroom-1`, `mushroom-card-mushroom-2`, etc.)

2. **Individual Tracking**: The browser can now track each card individually during transitions, allowing for much more sophisticated animations

3. **Smooth Movement**: When filtering from "All" to a specific category, cards that remain visible will smoothly move to their new positions instead of just appearing/disappearing

4. **Custom Animations**: Added slide-out-down and slide-in-up animations that make cards gracefully exit downward and enter upward

5. **Enhanced Timing**: Extended animation duration to 0.4s for the root transition and 0.3s for individual cards

## The Result:
Now when you filter the mushroom cards:
- Cards that are being hidden will slide down and fade out
- Cards that are being shown will slide up and fade in 
- Cards that remain visible will smoothly animate to their new grid positions
- The overall effect is much more polished and engaging than simple fade in/out

This creates a premium, app-like experience for your mushroom filtering functionality!
